'''Line 3''' of the [[Harbin Metro]] ({{zh|s=哈尔滨地铁三号线|p=Hārbīn Dìtiě Sān Hào Xiàn}}) is a [[rapid transit]] line in [[Harbin]], running from Harbinxizhan to Yidaeryuan. The line is 5.45 km long with 5 stations, all of which are underground, and it commenced operations on 26 January 2017. 

==History==
The first phase of the line, from Harbinxizhan to Yidaeryuan, commenced operations on 26 January 2017.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.focus.cn/hrb/2017-01-26/11372062.html |title=哈尔滨地铁3号线一期今日正式开通 附乘车票价表 |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=26 January 2017 |website=news.focus.cn |access-date=3 February 2018 |language=Chinese}}</ref>

Harbindajie station opened as an infill station on June 16, 2017. Harbindajie station renamed to Kaishengyuanguangchang station on March 20, 2019.

